text: Target () is a 2014 Chinese action suspense crime film directed by Yang Jiang. It was released on October 24. ==Cast== *Song Yang *Yang Juncheng *Kara Wang *Maria Makarenko *Ma Qiang *Ran Tian ==Reception== By November 3, the film had earned ¥1.57 million at the Chinese box office. ==References== Category:2014 crime action films Category:Chinese crime action films Category:Chinese films Category:English-language films Category:Mandarin-language films
